==计划与制作==
本剧第一次规划是在2011年10月于[[NBC|NBC]]的计划板（development slate）上出现的，但并不计划拍摄試播集（pilot order）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2011/10/03/development-update-monday-october-3-533511/9466/ |title=Development Update: Monday, October 3 |date=October 3, 2011 |publisher=[[The_Futon_Critic|The Futon Critic]] |accessdate=September 12, 2013 |archive-date=2020-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200904170813/http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2011/10/03/development-update-monday-october-3-533511/9466/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。在2012年8月，NBC决定重审当时名为'''''最后战役'''''(''The Last Stand'')的实验剧集剧本<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2012/08/03/development-update-friday-august-3-533420/9908/ |title=Development Update: Friday, August 3 |date=August 3, 2012 |publisher=[[The_Futon_Critic|The Futon Critic]] |accessdate=September 12, 2013}}</ref>。2012年10月8日，NBC电视台签订了实验剧集的拍摄，并启用新名字''After Hours''<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/nbc-orders-medical-drama-pilot-gabe-sachs-jeff-judah-377078 |title=NBC Orders Medical Drama Pilot from '90210' Writers |date=October 8, 2012 |last=O'Connell |first=Michael |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |accessdate=September 12, 2013 |archive-date=2020-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803184040/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/nbc-orders-medical-drama-pilot-gabe-sachs-jeff-judah-377078 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。实验剧集由Pierre Morel导演，Gabe Sachs与Jeff Judah编剧。

演员招募于2012年10月开始。约恩•马肯（Eoin Macken）首先拿到了T.C. Callahan这个角色。该角色是一名刚刚从军队退役且常与上司发生冲突的一名医生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/10/eoin-macken-to-star-in-nbc-pilot-after-hours/ |title=Eoin Macken To Star In NBC Pilot ‘After Hours’ |date=October 26, 2012 |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |accessdate=September 12, 2013 |archive-date=2014-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140724023604/http://www.deadline.com/2012/10/eoin-macken-to-star-in-nbc-pilot-after-hours/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 罗德•里格兹（Freddy Rodriues)是第二个拿到本剧角色的演员，在剧中饰演迈克尔•里格塔（Michael Ragosa)。该角色是本想成为一名外科手术医生但因为不可抗原因而成为医院的管理者。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2012/11/02/development-update-friday-november-2-863215/10044/ |title=Development Update: Friday, November 2 |date=November 2, 2012 |publisher=[[The_Futon_Critic|The Futon Critic]] |accessdate=September 12, 2013}}</ref>肯•梁与吉妮安•古森先后拿到剧中的角色。梁在剧中饰演陶福一角。该角色曾帮助过在战争中受伤的士兵，现担任圣安东尼奥医院急诊室医生职务。古森则签约饰演克丽丝塔一角，一个漂亮的实习医生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cinemablend.com/television/Lost-Ken-Leung-Jeananne-Goossen-Join-NBC-Hours-Pilot-49046.html |title=Lost's Ken Leung And Jeananne Goossen Join NBC's After Hours Pilot |date=November 6, 2012 |last=Rawden |first=Jessica |work=Cinema Blend |accessdate=September 12, 2013 |archive-date=2020-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204075128/https://www.cinemablend.com/television/Lost-Ken-Leung-Jeananne-Goossen-Join-NBC-Hours-Pilot-49046.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>在11月初，罗伯特•贝利加入了剧组，在剧中饰演一名名叫保罗•卡明斯的过于拘谨的实习医生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/11/pilots-those-who-kill-and-after-hours-add-regulars/ |title=Pilots ‘Those Who Kill’ And ‘After Hours’ Add Regulars |date=November 8, 2012 |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |accessdate=September 12, 2013 |archive-date=2014-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140724034711/http://www.deadline.com/2012/11/pilots-those-who-kill-and-after-hours-add-regulars/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 吉尔•弗林特是之后签约饰演Jordan Alexander的人。该角色是一名刚晋升的夜班管理员,并且与T.C. 约过会。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tvline.com/2012/11/09/after-hours-pilot-cast-jill-flint-doctor/ |title=Pilot Scoop: Royal Pains' Jill Flint Signs on to NBC Medical Drama After Hours |date=November 9, 2012 |last=Roots |first=Kimberly |publisher=[[TVLine|TVLine]] |accessdate=September 12, 2013 |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125040257/https://tvline.com/2012/11/09/after-hours-pilot-cast-jill-flint-doctor/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> Daniella Alonso是最后一个签约出演剧集的演员。她将在剧中饰演Dr. Landry de la Cruz一角。一名孤独的夜班心理医生。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/revolutions-daniella-alonso-joins-nbcs-592451 |title='Revolution's' Daniella Alonso Joins NBC's 'Night Shift' (Exclusive) |date=July 24, 2013 |last=Goldberg |first=Lesley |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |accessdate=September 12, 2013 |archive-date=2013-09-05 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6JPlgZv0S?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/revolutions-daniella-alonso-joins-nbcs-592451 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

